Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.57,0:15:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! Don't go pretending to be a proper husband \N{so casually} with another man's daughter! {kiyasuku is just "relaxed; familiar; easy to access; friendly" and I'm not sure why he can't be familiar with his own wife, so going liberal here, pairing it up with previous line to better explain his anger; 亭主顔するな - zura is some weird reading of kao, methinks it means "put up a play/feign innocent face"; lit is "don't behave like a household head; master/husband familiarly with a person's daughter [calling her mother]" - maybe he means "with my daughter right as I'm standing right here"; Any ideas how this mess can be improved, TLC?} {15:47: I'm hearing 貴様！人の娘に気安く亭主ずらするな\NI'm not entirely sure if this is right but this is what I'm hearing.\NIf it is right, then a possible TL would be something like " Bastard! Don't go acting like a husband so casually in front of another man's daughter!" - Au}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.49,0:15:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! Don't go pretending to be a proper husband \Nso casually in front of another man's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.61,0:15:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard! Don't go pretending to be a proper husband \Nso casually in front of another man's daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.74,0:15:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.58,0:16:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.20,0:16:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.01,0:16:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.27,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You were so friendly to us two, \Nwhy are you suddenly so hostile to dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.90,0:16:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Do something already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.19,0:16:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,And{act. just aite}... Taruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.82,0:16:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha... What's this? My body won't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.66,0:16:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.70,0:16:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Father, this is what Taru-chan can do with his magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.95,0:16:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Limpy-kun's buddy, Limpimpy. {warawarara - again, not sure if there's no pun to it}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:48.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If no picture at hand, \Ncan move people while you point at them. {/without a picture, person you just point your finger at obeys you}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.00,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see. You poor thing. \NThis vile man brainwashed you as well?! {hope it's "to inspire; to indoctrinate" but maybe just "heard/told you"}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.84,0:16:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that, grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruruuto is a real magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.26,0:17:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.35,0:17:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see, I see. Through your insidious influence, \Neven an ordinary child can mutate into some freak! {/thanks to you, even children become strange}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.20,0:17:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This - body manipulating magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.23,0:17:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.69,0:17:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it! It seems you can truly \Nwield some magic, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, alright? \NNow make this magic leave me alone! {really unsure what's this toite in the end}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.19,0:17:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure! 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.79,0:17:29.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. A magician! How most unusual... {/amazing isn't it}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.42,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Me unusual.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked! Grandpa's resentment subsided! {/anger is under control}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.91,0:17:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That may be so for now,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.63,0:17:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but don't think I'll ever forgive your despicable ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.47,0:17:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.98,0:17:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Show this wreck of a man the door! {mezawari is "eyesore; unpleasant sight; obstructing a view"} {/kick him out}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.75,0:17:43.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\3c&H4A265C&} Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.51,0:17:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minute, father, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.29,0:17:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me have a say, too! {/I have a story}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.40,0:17:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You prick! Stop resisting! {/come/go out sooner}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.62,0:18:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.96,0:18:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.00,0:18:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Your last chance to get out of my sight! {/disappear from before me}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My daughter and my grandson \Nare staying here with me! {/will live together with me here}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.85,0:18:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Father! Please come to your senses! {/stop being unreasonable/mad}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.16,0:18:25.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.56,0:18:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone needs to stop him! {this doesn't really seem that shocking a line to cause such a reaction from him, but I don't see a way to make it more sensible}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.63,0:18:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.94,0:18:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Where could she be?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.50,0:18:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mother died last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,She was sure she would get to see you again someday, \Nand was looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.83,0:18:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, last winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.63,0:18:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,all of a sudden, she fell ill. {btw, it was heart attack in manga}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since you left, she was feeling lonely, \Nmany days passed by without any progress. {/it was getting worse with every day passing} {lit: continuing every day - im not really sure what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, without ever finding out where you are... {/your whereabouts/address}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.68,0:19:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma... died?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.10,0:19:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.19,0:19:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't pity myself. \NHowever, if it's her... {lit: I'm good, but the other party/her}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko's fate is breaking my heart. {fubin is "poor; pitiful; piteous; pitiable" - I hope this is what he means - Mitsuko endured a lot of pitiable misery}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And all of that... {/this and that}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,All our misfortunes are his doing! {/everything is bastard's fault}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.91,0:19:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.37,0:19:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The price for my happy life up until now \Nhas been a grudge amassing in other people! {/While I was living my life happy and carefree, everyone was suffering so much}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Taru! Use some magic to reconcile everyone! {/you have to make everyone get along with magic}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.71,0:19:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Taruru... oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru, when in doubt, \Nask Tama-chan for advice. {/in times of trouble you can ask tama}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.01,0:19:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Good call! Tama-chan, we need your wisdom! {/please do/counting on you}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.51,0:19:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me just a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.60,0:19:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, Taru-chan. \NItako-chan might help you now. {act. she just says "if you put out ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.87,0:19:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.68,0:19:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Tama-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.85,0:19:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,200)}Itako, Ittaro, Taruru and{/'s} ru...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.70,0:19:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Taruru!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.16,0:20:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's you, darling? It's you, isn't it? {guess, hope it's anata but no clue for the rest. TLC?} {20:10: I'm hearing あなたね、あなた\NA possible TL could be "That is you, darling, isn't it?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.21,0:20:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been half a year. {/we haven't seen in ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.34,0:20:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you doing well? {/have you been ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.24,0:20:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko! But how... {/why/what's going on to you}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:28.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This is supposed to be grandma? \NIsn't she a bit young for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.85,0:20:32.63,Default,,0,0,0,,This - Spiritual TV-phone, \Nallowing to talk to the otherworld. {霊界テレビ電話}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.63,0:20:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello-hello Itako-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.40,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no age in otherworld. {lit: that world, years unrelated/irrelevant}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.30,0:20:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, my life here has been full of delights. {/I lead a happy life here}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.14,0:20:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you worry for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.32,0:20:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Instead, if you really want to make me happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.53,0:20:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,leave behind your fixation on revenge \Nand learn to forgive people around you. {/But if you're thinking of me, you shouldn't be so angry and resentful.}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.62,0:20:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Shogunosuke-san meant no harm. \NI want you to start getting along with him. {/forgive ..., and please reconcile}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.00,0:20:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,All our efforts should be directed \Non making everyone get along! {/I want everyone to make effort to get along}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.75,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Only then you can ensure that one day \Nyou and me will once again be reunited up here. {/by doing so, you guarantee that someday, when here, you'll definitely be living together with me again}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.03,0:21:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.09,0:21:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I got it. Forgive...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.82,0:21:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will forgive, Mitsuko. {unsure, maybe he means "Forgive me"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.70,0:21:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru, Honmaru, \NI have no doubt you guys will live a happy life. {/will definitely become happy}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember that I'm always watching over you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.95,0:21:26.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.29,0:21:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuko!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.05,0:21:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandpa. This ain't as magnificent a feast \Nas they serve at your place, {goshisou is "gorgeous dinner; feast; excellent food; special dish; delicacy" so either "it's not as sophisticated as ..." or "not as big as ..."}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but you still shouldn't hesitate to eat. {hope it's enryosezu - "without reserve; constraint; restraint; modesty; diffidence; hesitation; holding back; discretion; tact; thoughtfulness"}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:54.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.49,0:21:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Chizuru, you've become infinitely better at cooking! {/you became better at ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.92,0:22:00.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Honmaru mama's cooking is superb!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.02,0:22:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Glad you liked it. Thanks. {/I'm happy}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.30,0:22:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Agreed. Our mom's cooking is unrivaled. {/the best}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.83,0:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.72,0:22:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's still some tension between them. {/still somehow awkward; clumsy; stiff; crude; unrefined; constrained}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.51,0:22:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.32,0:22:46.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's snowing, snowing! \NHurry up and let's go outside! {/wake up/get up sooner}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.57,0:22:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on! Don't you know it's cold outside, Taru?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.66,0:22:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Honmaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.08,0:22:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.59,0:22:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.20,0:22:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlewarm-kun, then? \NThe name is kinda self-explanatory. {/he even has a name}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.66,0:22:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.25,0:22:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Magical Taruruuto-kun:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.96,0:23:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dangerous Snowball Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.32,0:23:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Children are as free as the wind! \NPlaying outside all togetheru-ru! {hope its kazenoko - outdoor creatures}
